messages.speech:
Child care grant applications are available after July 1 for each award year.   The basic qualifications are:

    Complete the FAFSA application
    Must be a Minnesota resident
    Must be registered for 6 or more credits
    Your child or children must in the care of a paid child care provider 

The application is here:
https://www.century.edu/sites/default/files/FinancialAid_ChildcareGrantApp_17-18.pdf
